sshsentinel
===========

sshsentinal  is  a  daemon  that  monitors  a  log  file  for  remote  break-in
attempts. It uses  a user customizable regular expression  to identify break-in
attempts and calls a script or other suitable application.

For more information refer to the man page.


Installation
------------

Refer to the INSTALL file


